method.description:
Listens to the element event with name [param event_id].
[param listener] is called with a [class Dictionary] with the information about the event along with the following keys:
[code]type[/code]: The type of the event, is equal to [param event_id];
[code]target_element[/code]: The target element which first triggered the event;
[code]current_element[/code]: Current element which receives the event;
Along with the event information, you can stop propagation of the event adding the key [code]stop_propagation[/code] or [code]stop_immediate_propagation[/code] to [code]true[/code].
